{"id":4704,"date":"2024-04-27T10:11:32","date_gmt":"2024-04-27T10:11:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/?p=4704"},"modified":"2024-04-27T10:35:08","modified_gmt":"2024-04-27T10:35:08","slug":"10-loi-ich-cua-viec-hoc-am-nhac-doi-voi-tre-em","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/10-loi-ich-cua-viec-hoc-am-nhac-doi-voi-tre-em\/","title":{"rendered":"10 L\u1ee3i \u00cdch C\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7c H\u1ecdc \u00c2m Nh\u1ea1c \u0110\u1ed1i V\u1edbi Tr\u1ebb Em"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>\u00c2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e2u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a tr\u1ebb. T\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c n\u00e2ng cao k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea1t, \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em, ch\u1ee9ng minh t\u1ea1i sao \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c n\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb.<\/p>\n<h4>1. <strong>C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng Ng\u00f4n Ng\u1eef v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ecdc Vi\u1ebft<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. \u00c2m nh\u1ea1c gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u1ed1n t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t \u00e2m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p. Tr\u1ebb em tham gia h\u1ecdc nh\u1ea1c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1ebd c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecdc v\u00e0 vi\u1ebft t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n do \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4710\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4710\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4710\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Ngon-Ngu-va-Doc-Viet.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng Ng\u00f4n Ng\u1eef v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ecdc Vi\u1ebft\" width=\"940\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Ngon-Ngu-va-Doc-Viet.jpg 940w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Ngon-Ngu-va-Doc-Viet-627x400.jpg 627w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Ngon-Ngu-va-Doc-Viet-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Ngon-Ngu-va-Doc-Viet-600x383.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4710\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng Ng\u00f4n Ng\u1eef v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ecdc Vi\u1ebft<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4>2. <strong>T\u0103ng C\u01b0\u1eddng K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng To\u00e1n H\u1ecdc<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>C\u00f3 m\u1ed1i li\u00ean h\u1ec7 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft gi\u1eefa \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c v\u00e0 to\u00e1n h\u1ecdc. \u00c2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em gi\u00fap ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1eabu nh\u1ecbp, \u0111\u1ebfm nh\u1ecbp v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac nh\u1ea1c. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc to\u00e1n, gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 to\u00e1n h\u1ecdc ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4717\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4717\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4717\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Ky-Nang-Toan-Hoc.jpg\" alt=\"T\u0103ng C\u01b0\u1eddng K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng To\u00e1n H\u1ecdc\" width=\"940\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Ky-Nang-Toan-Hoc.jpg 940w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Ky-Nang-Toan-Hoc-627x400.jpg 627w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Ky-Nang-Toan-Hoc-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Ky-Nang-Toan-Hoc-600x383.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4717\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u0103ng C\u01b0\u1eddng K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng To\u00e1n H\u1ecdc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4>3. <strong>Ph\u00e1t Tri\u1ec3n K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng X\u00e3 H\u1ed9i<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>\u00c2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. Khi tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m nh\u1ea1c ho\u1eb7c d\u00e0n nh\u1ea1c, tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nh\u00f3m, l\u1eafng nghe \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i. \u00c2m nh\u1ea1c gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb em h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch chia s\u1ebb, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng quan tr\u1ecdng cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4715\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4715\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4715\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Phat-Trien-Ky-Nang-Xa-Hoi.jpg\" alt=\"Ph\u00e1t Tri\u1ec3n K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng X\u00e3 H\u1ed9i\" width=\"940\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Phat-Trien-Ky-Nang-Xa-Hoi.jpg 940w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Phat-Trien-Ky-Nang-Xa-Hoi-627x400.jpg 627w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Phat-Trien-Ky-Nang-Xa-Hoi-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Phat-Trien-Ky-Nang-Xa-Hoi-600x383.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4715\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00e1t Tri\u1ec3n K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng X\u00e3 H\u1ed9i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4>4. <strong>C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng V\u1eadn \u0110\u1ed9ng<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>Ch\u01a1i nh\u1ea1c c\u1ee5 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng tinh. \u00c2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p tay m\u1eaft, k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n tay v\u00e0 ng\u00f3n tay kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi ch\u01a1i c\u00e1c nh\u1ea1c c\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 piano, guitar, ho\u1eb7c violin. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u1eefu \u00edch cho vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i nh\u1ea1c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i trong c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4711\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4711\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4711\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Van-Dong-1.jpg\" alt=\"C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng V\u1eadn \u0110\u1ed9ng\" width=\"940\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Van-Dong-1.jpg 940w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Van-Dong-1-627x400.jpg 627w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Van-Dong-1-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Cai-Thien-Ky-Nang-Van-Dong-1-600x383.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4711\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n K\u1ef9 N\u0103ng V\u1eadn \u0110\u1ed9ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4>5. <strong>Gi\u1ea3m Stress v\u00e0 C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n S\u1ee9c Kh\u1ecfe T\u00e2m Th\u1ea7n<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>\u00c2m nh\u1ea1c c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m stress. \u00c2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em gi\u00fap ch\u00fang th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecdc nh\u1ea1c c\u0169ng gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb em ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u khi ch\u00fang h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n nh\u1ea1c ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c c\u1ee5 m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4712\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4712\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4712\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Giam-Stress-va-Cai-Thien-Suc-Khoe-Tam-Than.jpg\" alt=\"Gi\u1ea3m Stress v\u00e0 C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n S\u1ee9c Kh\u1ecfe T\u00e2m Th\u1ea7n\" width=\"940\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Giam-Stress-va-Cai-Thien-Suc-Khoe-Tam-Than.jpg 940w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Giam-Stress-va-Cai-Thien-Suc-Khoe-Tam-Than-627x400.jpg 627w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Giam-Stress-va-Cai-Thien-Suc-Khoe-Tam-Than-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Giam-Stress-va-Cai-Thien-Suc-Khoe-Tam-Than-600x383.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4712\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gi\u1ea3m Stress v\u00e0 C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n S\u1ee9c Kh\u1ecfe T\u00e2m Th\u1ea7n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4>6. <strong>T\u0103ng C\u01b0\u1eddng Kh\u1ea3 N\u0103ng T\u1eadp Trung v\u00e0 T\u1ef1 Gi\u00e1c<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>Tr\u1ebb em h\u1ecdc \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung cao \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang nh\u1ecbp v\u00e0 theo k\u1ecbp b\u1ea3n nh\u1ea1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec c\u1ee7a tr\u1ebb. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c c\u0169ng gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 gi\u00e1c khi ch\u00fang t\u1ef1 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i nh\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4716\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4716\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4716\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Kha-Nang-Tap-Trung-va-Tu-Giac.jpg\" alt=\"T\u0103ng C\u01b0\u1eddng Kh\u1ea3 N\u0103ng T\u1eadp Trung v\u00e0 T\u1ef1 Gi\u00e1c\" width=\"940\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Kha-Nang-Tap-Trung-va-Tu-Giac.jpg 940w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Kha-Nang-Tap-Trung-va-Tu-Giac-627x400.jpg 627w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Kha-Nang-Tap-Trung-va-Tu-Giac-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Tang-Cuong-Kha-Nang-Tap-Trung-va-Tu-Giac-600x383.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4716\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u0103ng C\u01b0\u1eddng Kh\u1ea3 N\u0103ng T\u1eadp Trung v\u00e0 T\u1ef1 Gi\u00e1c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4>7. <strong>Khuy\u1ebfn Kh\u00edch S\u1ef1 S\u00e1ng T\u1ea1o v\u00e0 T\u01b0\u1edfng T\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>\u00c2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tr\u1ebb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh qua \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c, s\u00e1ng t\u00e1c giai \u0111i\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c vi\u1ebft l\u1eddi b\u00e0i h\u00e1t. S\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n trong \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb tr\u1edf n\u00ean linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n trong m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4713\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4713\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4713\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Khuyen-Khich-Su-Sang-Tao-va-Tuong-Tuong.jpg\" alt=\"Khuy\u1ebfn Kh\u00e