 srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Phat-Trien-Cam-Giac-Tham-My.jpg 940w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Phat-Trien-Cam-Giac-Tham-My-627x400.jpg 627w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Phat-Trien-Cam-Giac-Tham-My-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Phat-Trien-Cam-Giac-Tham-My-600x383.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4714\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00e1t Tri\u1ec3n C\u1ea3m Gi\u00e1c Th\u1ea9m M\u1ef9<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4>9. <strong>Th\u00fac \u0110\u1ea9y T\u00ednh \u0110\u1ed9c L\u1eadp v\u00e0 Tr\u00e1ch Nhi\u1ec7m<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>Khi tr\u1ebb tham gia v\u00e0o c\u00e1c kh\u00f3a h\u1ecdc \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c, tr\u1ebb h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 l\u1eadp v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tr\u1ebb ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng cao t\u00ednh t\u1ef1 l\u1eadp v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4709\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4709\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4709\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Thuc-Day-Tinh-Doc-Lap-va-Trach-Nhiem.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u00fac \u0110\u1ea9y T\u00ednh \u0110\u1ed9c L\u1eadp v\u00e0 Tr\u00e1ch Nhi\u1ec7m\" width=\"940\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Thuc-Day-Tinh-Doc-Lap-va-Trach-Nhiem.jpg 940w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Thuc-Day-Tinh-Doc-Lap-va-Trach-Nhiem-627x400.jpg 627w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Thuc-Day-Tinh-Doc-Lap-va-Trach-Nhiem-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Thuc-Day-Tinh-Doc-Lap-va-Trach-Nhiem-600x383.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4709\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u00fac \u0110\u1ea9y T\u00ednh \u0110\u1ed9c L\u1eadp v\u00e0 Tr\u00e1ch Nhi\u1ec7m<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h4>10. <strong>N\u00e2ng Cao Kh\u1ea3 N\u0103ng L\u1eafng Nghe v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed3ng C\u1ea3m<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>\u00c2m nh\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1ebb em c\u0169ng gi\u00fap ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u1eafng nghe v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m. Tr\u1ebb h\u1ecdc c\u00e1ch l\u1eafng nghe k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng khi ch\u01a1i nh\u1ea1c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean kh\u00e1c trong d\u00e0n nh\u1ea1c. Nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u00e2m nh\u1ea1c m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong giao ti\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4708\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4708\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4708\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Nang-Cao-Kha-Nang-Lang-Nghe-va-Dong-Cam.jpg\" alt=\"N\u00e2ng Cao Kh\u1ea3 N\u0103ng L\u1eafng Nghe v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed3ng C\u1ea3m\" width=\"940\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Nang-Cao-Kha-Nang-Lang-Nghe-va-Dong-Cam.jpg 940w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Nang-Cao-Kha-Nang-Lang-Nghe-va-Dong-Cam-627x400.jpg 627w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Nang-Cao-Kha-Nang-Lang-Nghe-va-Dong-Cam-768x490.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/Nang-Cao-Kha-Nang-Lang-Nghe-va-Dong-Cam-600x383.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940p